        {
            "id": 6007494,
            "title": "魏哲家喊話十年無虞！這幾檔受惠股即將噴出？",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"348\" data-mime=\"image/png\" data-ratio=\"2.1839080459770117\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6007494/m/12fadb08741425d0aead421be7cf1539.jpg\" data-width=\"760\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6007494/l/12fadb08741425d0aead421be7cf1539.jpg\"/></figure></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007494%2Fl%2Fa5119c2a9e3e9763479bb93a264c0ab0.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007494%2Fl%2Fa5119c2a9e3e9763479bb93a264c0ab0.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007494%2Fl%2Fa5119c2a9e3e9763479bb93a264c0ab0.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007494%2Fl%2Fa5119c2a9e3e9763479bb93a264c0ab0.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007494%2Fl%2Fa5119c2a9e3e9763479bb93a264c0ab0.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007494%2Fl%2Fa5119c2a9e3e9763479bb93a264c0ab0.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007494%2Fl%2Fa5119c2a9e3e9763479bb93a264c0ab0.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007494%2Fl%2Fa5119c2a9e3e9763479bb93a264c0ab0.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007494%2Fl%2Fa5119c2a9e3e9763479bb93a264c0ab0.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007494%2Fl%2Fa5119c2a9e3e9763479bb93a264c0ab0.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007494%2Fl%2Fa5119c2a9e3e9763479bb93a264c0ab0.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007494%2Fl%2Fa5119c2a9e3e9763479bb93a264c0ab0.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007494%2Fl%2Fa5119c2a9e3e9763479bb93a264c0ab0.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007494%2Fl%2Fa5119c2a9e3e9763479bb93a264c0ab0.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007494%2Fl%2Fa5119c2a9e3e9763479bb93a264c0ab0.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007494%2Fl%2Fa5119c2a9e3e9763479bb93a264c0ab0.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007494%2Fl%2Fa5119c2a9e3e9763479bb93a264c0ab0.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">魏哲家喊話十年無虞！這幾檔受惠股即將噴出？(圖:shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近期，美國前總統川普的關稅政策再度成為全球市場關注焦點。從 4 月 2 日針對全球發起「對等關稅」開始，一連串的懲罰性調漲與政策暫緩，令全球供應鏈與投資人無所適從。然而，隨著美國聯邦法院於日前正式裁定，川普的對等關稅違反美國憲政體制中的貿易授權程序，整體情勢出現轉機。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>儘管川普已提出上訴，但作為一個民主法治國家，美國的司法系統具備強而有力的制衡機制。預計在下週一（6 月 9 日），法院將針對上訴做出最終裁定，而持續判決違法的機率依然偏高。即使川普手中仍握有 301 條款等法律工具，個別州政府已陸續提起訴訟。綜合而言，未來川普實施的關稅政策，很可能將低於市場原先預期，這對全球貿易環境與股市都是正面訊號。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"348\" data-mime=\"image/png\" data-ratio=\"2.1839080459770117\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6007494/m/5f23485e1896ed3e044184bcca1c33e0.jpg\" data-width=\"760\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6007494/l/5f23485e1896ed3e044184bcca1c33e0.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>市場也已提前反應此一利多，美股四大指數全面反彈，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊</a>、<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">那斯達克</a>大漲，德國 DAX 指數更持續改寫歷史新高。台股與美股連動性高，自然也同步受惠。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"428\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.7757009345794392\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6007494/m/4b54d5b6a0af19b547d8aa23271b5594.jpg\" data-width=\"760\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6007494/l/4b54d5b6a0af19b547d8aa23271b5594.jpg\" srcset=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6007494/l/4b54d5b6a0af19b547d8aa23271b5594.jpg 1x,https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6007494/xl/4b54d5b6a0af19b547d8aa23271b5594.jpg 2x,https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6007494/xxl/4b54d5b6a0af19b547d8aa23271b5594.jpg 3x\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>在這樣的背景下，台灣最具代表性的權值股——台積電，於本週股東會中釋出強烈信心訊號。董事長魏哲家明確表示，未來十年台積電營運將持續成長，並直言「建議大家多買台積電」。公司同時指出，儘管持續擴大在美投資，但每年資本支出維持在 400 億美元以上，且不影響核心先進製程布局。2 奈米、1.4 奈米技術如期推進；此外，AI 應用與人形機器人相關晶片已開始實際貢獻營收，與 AI 霸主輝達的合作也更加深化。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>在產業結構上，AI、高速運算與智慧製造將成為中長線主流，相關類股持續受資金青睞。近期如廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>)、技嘉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2376:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2376\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2376-TW</a>)、緯穎(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6669:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6669\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6669-TW</a>)、台光電(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2383:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2383\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2383-TW</a>)、奇鋐(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3017:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3017\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3017-TW</a>) 等個股，表現都相當強勢，股價接連挑戰波段高點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"428\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.7757009345794392\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6007494/m/ebf1e0e1f1db2b5ef4dd79033176bb16.jpg\" data-width=\"760\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6007494/l/ebf1e0e1f1db2b5ef4dd79033176bb16.jpg\" srcset=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6007494/l/ebf1e0e1f1db2b5ef4dd79033176bb16.jpg 1x,https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6007494/xl/ebf1e0e1f1db2b5ef4dd79033176bb16.jpg 2x,https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6007494/xxl/ebf1e0e1f1db2b5ef4dd79033176bb16.jpg 3x\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>至於有哪些個股還沒漲、或正準備起漲？投資人可點擊下方連結，輸入「888」，即可取得完整名單與觀察重點，不讓下一波主流行情擦身而過。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>➤鼎極操盤手 何基鼎 LINE 粉絲團</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://lin.ee/iuxMCJU\">https://lin.ee/iuxMCJU</a></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>➤鼎極操盤手 何基鼎 YT</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@gd1788\">https://www.youtube.com/@gd1788</a></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"428\" data-mime=\"image/png\" data-ratio=\"1.7757009345794392\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6007494/m/7025d48f4b2203f79c0d06206388c7d1.jpg\" data-width=\"760\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6007494/l/7025d48f4b2203f79c0d06206388c7d1.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"warning\">本公司所推薦分析之個別有價證券<br/>\n無不當之財務利益關係 以往之績效不保證未來獲利<br/>\n投資人應獨立判斷 審慎評估並自負投資風險</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
